WEBVTT

1
00:01:08.068 --> 00:01:10.195
<font color="#fecb00">I want to talk to someone in charge!</font>

2
00:01:11.488 --> 00:01:12.738
<font color="#fecb00"><i>My father is</i></font>

3
00:01:12.739 --> 00:01:14.157
<font color="#fecb00"><i>Hiroshi Randa!</i></font>

4
00:01:14.825 --> 00:01:15.825
<font color="#fecb00"><i>Randa!</i></font>

5
00:34:40.998 --> 00:34:43.583
<font color="#fecb00">Get out of my way.</font>

6
00:34:56.679 --> 00:34:59.516
<font color="#fecb00">Tastes so good! This is it.</font>

7
00:35:18.368 --> 00:35:20.454
<font color="#fecb00"><i>What is the secret of the triangle shape?</i></font>

8
00:35:22.372 --> 00:35:24.957
<font color="#fecb00"><i>The secret of deliciousness is...</i></font>

9
00:35:24.958 --> 00:35:26.292
<font color="#fecb00"><i>I'm not going to tell you!</i></font>

10
00:35:26.293 --> 00:35:27.669
<font color="#fecb00"><i>Tada!</i></font>

11
00:38:22.261 --> 00:38:23.637
<font color="#fecb00">You’ll be all right.</font>

12
00:38:25.848 --> 00:38:27.558
<font color="#fecb00">I’m sorry. Cate.</font>

13
00:38:28.725 --> 00:38:30.852
<font color="#fecb00">But you are strong.</font>

14
00:38:30.853 --> 00:38:32.896
<font color="#fecb00">You’ll be all right.</font>
